section.def:
balance
                (結餘) includes, where applicable, money ledger
            balance;

paragraph.content:
during a monthly accounting period, an associated entity of the
                    intermediary is required to prepare and provide to the client a receipt in
                    accordance with section 13;

subparagraph.content:
the quantity, description and such other particulars of the client
                        assets or security as are sufficient to enable them to be
                        identified;
